data.title: What song from 1987 is more famous, "Sweet Child O'Mine" by Guns N'Roses or "Livin on a Prayer" by Bon Jovi?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 9): I would say “Sweet Child O’ Mine”. Sheryl Crow did a cover (for the Adam Sandler film Big Daddy), which, while rather tepidly regarded, did win Crow a Grammy.
